DELICATESKIN  
Sheep oil deeply moisturizes and penetrates the skin  
Extracts skin-friendly components from wool  
Fine  
What is sheep oil?  
Sheep oil refers to lanolin, which is similar to the skin's protective layer components. It provides protection, moisturizes the skin, hydrates dry skin, and enhances skin moisture.

绵羊油是指羊毛脂，于肌肤保护层成分相似，能为肌肤提供保护，水润肌肤，湿润干燥肌肤，提升肌肤水分。
